flowchart TD
    Start(["💻 Developer<br/>Commits Code"]) --> PreCommit["🔒 Pre-commit Hooks<br/>gitleaks secret scan<br/><br/>Blocks commit if secrets found"]

    PreCommit --> Trigger{{"🔀 Build<br/>Trigger"}}

    Trigger -->|"UBI Path"| BuildUBI["🔨 Build UBI Image<br/>Multi-stage Containerfile<br/><br/>• npm audit (FAIL on HIGH/CRITICAL)<br/>• Multi-arch (AMD64+ARM64)<br/>• Base: ubi9/nodejs-20"]
    Trigger -->|"RHHI Path"| BuildRHHI["🔨 Build RHHI Image<br/>Multi-stage Containerfile<br/><br/>• npm audit (FAIL on HIGH/CRITICAL)<br/>• Multi-arch (AMD64+ARM64)<br/>• Base: hi/nodejs:20-builder"]

    BuildUBI --> SecretUBI["🔐 Trivy Secret Scan<br/>FAIL on HIGH/CRITICAL<br/><br/>Detects hardcoded credentials"]
    BuildRHHI --> SecretRHHI["🔐 Trivy Secret Scan<br/>FAIL on HIGH/CRITICAL<br/><br/>Detects hardcoded credentials"]

    SecretUBI --> ScanUBI["🛡️ Trivy CVE Scan<br/>Report HIGH/CRITICAL<br/><br/>UBI: 7 CVEs (RHEL 9.7)"]
    SecretRHHI --> ScanRHHI["🛡️ Trivy CVE Scan<br/>Report HIGH/CRITICAL<br/><br/>RHHI: Minimal (distroless) ⭐"]

    ScanUBI --> SBOMU["📋 Generate SBOM<br/>CycloneDX JSON<br/><br/>Supply chain transparency"]
    ScanRHHI --> SBOMR["📋 Generate SBOM<br/>CycloneDX JSON<br/><br/>Supply chain transparency"]

    SBOMU --> PushUBI["⬆️ Push to Registry<br/>ghcr.io/jkirklan/<br/>demo-*-ubi:latest"]
    SBOMR --> PushRHHI["⬆️ Push to Registry<br/>ghcr.io/jkirklan/<br/>demo-*-rhhi:latest"]

    PushUBI --> Deploy["🚀 Deploy via Quadlet<br/>Podman + systemd"]
    PushRHHI --> Deploy

    Deploy --> Verify["✅ Verify<br/>Health checks<br/>Smoke tests"]

    classDef startEnd fill:#e1f5ff,stroke:#01579b,stroke-width:2px
